              "displayName": "Carlo Curino",
              "active": true,
              "timeZone": "Etc/UTC"
            },
            "body": "We had a simple implementation for this, using QueueMetrics and maintaining a map of delays (using SampleQuantile), tracking start-end \nof the wait-time by catching reserve() and unreserve() calls.  In our test environment, it didn't seem to matter much. \n\nWe might further investigate, and post patches after YARN-1051 is committed.",
